set incsearch "Make search act like search in modern browsers

" .h files
:autocmd BufNewFile *.h MkGuard

" JSON
au! BufRead,BufNewFile *.json setfiletype javascript

"sandvine policy
autocmd BufNewFile,BufRead policy*.conf set filetype=sandvine
